Package: GenesPackage
Type: Package
Title: Genes Management Package
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Arianna", "Rigamonti", email = "arianna1.rigamonti@mail.polimi.it", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A package to manage gene information using S4 classes and GenomicRanges. 
    It provides a comprehensive suite for handling different gene types, including 
    protein-coding genes and various non-coding RNA genes. The package supports 
    operations such as creation, modification, and summary of gene objects.
Depends: R (>= 4.4.0)
Imports: methods, GenomicRanges, IRanges
